DOCUMENT();        # This should be the first executable line in the problem.

loadMacros(
"PG.pl",
"PGbasicmacros.pl",
"PGchoicemacros.pl",
"PGanswermacros.pl",
"PGauxiliaryFunctions.pl"
);

TEXT(&beginproblem);
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a = random(2,5,1);
$b = random(2,5,1);
$c = random(2,5,1);
$d = random(2,5,1);
$e = random(2,5,1);
$f = random(2,5,1);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
The expression \((3a^$a b^$b c^$c)^2(2a^$d b^$e c^$f)^3\) equals
\(na^rb^sc^t\) $BR where \(n\), the leading coefficient, is:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans = 72;
&ANS(strict_num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and \(r\), the exponent of \(a\), is:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans =$a*2+$d*3;
&ANS(strict_num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and \(s\), the exponent of \(b\), is:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans =$b*2+$e*3;
&ANS(strict_num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and finally \(t\), the exponent of \(c\), is:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
[NOTE:  Your answers cannot be algebraic expressions.]
$BR
EOT

$ans =$c*2+$f*3;
&ANS(strict_num_cmp($ans));

ENDDOCUMENT();        # This should be the last executable line in the problem.
